  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    NEFFICS Platform: Mentor&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The NEFFICS Platform is the integrated set of tools offered by the NEFFICS project. The platform consists of the&#xD;
    following tools:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
        href=&quot;./../../../core.default.tool_def.extend_neffics-sintef/tools/neffics_business_model_canvas_5C760C66.html&quot;&#xD;
        guid=&quot;_TUIRsLSjEeGOSY51NyhYZA&quot;>NEFFICS Business Model Canvas&lt;/a>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
        href=&quot;./../../../core.default.tool_def.extend_neffics-sintef/tools/neffics_innovation_cloud_F333CCD8.html&quot;&#xD;
        guid=&quot;_hmpioLb0EeGSldvlqRCwfg&quot;>NEFFICS Innovation Cloud&lt;/a>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
        href=&quot;./../../../core.default.tool_def.extend_neffics-sintef/tools/neffics_business_operations_platform_862EEB6D.html&quot;&#xD;
         guid=&quot;_mPjncLb0EeGSldvlqRCwfg&quot;>NEFFICS Business Operations Platform&lt;/a>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
        href=&quot;./../../../core.default.tool_def.extend_neffics-sintef/tools/neffics_service_modelling_editor_28DB3D61.html&quot;&#xD;
        guid=&quot;_hPs4kLX_EeGFxaC4r7U9rA&quot;>NEFFICS Service Modelling Editor&lt;/a>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
        href=&quot;./../../../core.default.tool_def.extend_neffics-sintef/tools/neffics_methodology_wiki_CEC2429C.html&quot;&#xD;
        guid=&quot;_MZ2doCdWEeKDGNEPRzZzCg&quot;>NEFFICS Methology Wiki&lt;/a>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The figure below&amp;nbsp;illustrates the architecture of the NEFFICS platform as a traditional multi-layered architecture,&#xD;
    consisting of three logical layers. Starting from the bottom we have:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        The &lt;strong>Platform Infrastructure&lt;/strong> layer consists of the platform components providing the Innovation&#xD;
        Community Infrastructure (by Induct in WP6), the Business Operations Platform (BOP) Infrastructure (by Cordys in&#xD;
        WP7), the Web-based Modelling and Method Framework Infrastructure (by SINTEF in WP5), and the Cloud Infrastructure&#xD;
        to access and integrate other cloud-based resources and services.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        The &lt;strong>Service and Application&lt;/strong> layer provides the Social Collaboration Platform running on top of the&#xD;
        Platform Infrastructure and comprises the Innovation Process Management and Composite Application Framework (in&#xD;
        BOP), including Customer-built Applications (from WP1 and WP2), and methods and guidelines developed in NEFFICS to&#xD;
        support networked innovation and business operations.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        The &lt;strong>Users&lt;/strong> layer manages the interaction with different user types (e.g. customer, employee,&#xD;
        stakeholder, network, vision/mission) through Web-Front Ends that provides access to cloud-based services from&#xD;
        Service and Application layer.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
